                            <comment id="12708482" author="bryanduxbury" created="Tue, 12 May 2009 16:06:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch disables the switching of native method tables. This appears to alleviate the problem in my tests. It might be slower than the original implementation, but I&apos;d rather have this fixed and get back to the speedup problem in another issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
